<div class="row justify-content-center">
  <div class="col-12 col-md-8 col-lg-7">
    <div class="card shadow border-0 rounded-4">
      <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white py-3">
        <h4 class="mb-0 text-center">
          <i class="bi bi-person-plus-fill"></i>
          Registro de Usuario
        </h4>
      </div>

      <div class="card-body p-4">

        <form action="/user/register-user" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">

          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
              <label for="name-input" class="form-label fw-bold">
                Nombre
              </label>
              <input type="text" class="form-control" id="name-input" name="firstName" value="{{firstName}}"
                placeholder="Ej: Juan" required />
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
              <label for="lastName-input" class="form-label fw-bold">
                Apellido
              </label>
              <input type="text" class="form-control" id="lastName-input" name="lastName" value="{{lastName}}"
                placeholder="Ej: Pérez" required />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
              <label for="phone-input" class="form-label fw-bold">
                Número de Teléfono
              </label>
              <input type="text" class="form-control" id="phone-input" name="phone" value="{{phone}}"
                placeholder="Ej: 809-555-5555" required />
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
              <label for="email-input" class="form-label fw-bold">
                Correo Electrónico
              </label>
              <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email-input" name="email" value="{{email}}"
                placeholder="correo@ejemplo.com" required />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mb-3">
            <label for="profilePicture-input" class="form-label fw-bold">
              Foto de Perfil
            </label>
            <input type="file" class="form-control" id="profilePicture-input" name="profilePicture"
              accept="image/png, image/jpeg, image/jpg" required />
            <small class="text-muted">
              Formatos permitidos: JPG, JPEG y PNG
            </small>
          </div>

          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
              <label for="username-input" class="form-label fw-bold">
                Nombre de Usuario
              </label>
              <input type="text" class="form-control" id="username-input" name="username" value="{{username}}"
                placeholder="Ej: juanperez01" required />
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
              <label for="role-input" class="form-label fw-bold">
                Registrarse como
              </label>
              <select class="form-select" id="role-input" name="role" required>
                <option value="">Seleccione un rol</option>

                <option value="client" {{#if (Equals role "client" )}}selected{{/if}}>
                  Cliente
                </option>

                <option value="delivery" {{#if (Equals role "delivery" )}}selected{{/if}}>
                  Repartidor
                </option>
              </select>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
              <label for="password-input" class="form-label fw-bold">
                Contraseña
              </label>
              <input type="password" class="form-control" id="password-input" name="password" minlength="8"
                placeholder="••••••••" required />
              <small class="text-muted">
                Mínimo 8 caracteres
              </small>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
              <label for="confirm-password-input" class="form-label fw-bold">
                Confirmar Contraseña
              </label>
              <input type="password" class="form-control" id="confirm-password-input" name="confirmPassword"
                minlength="8" placeholder="••••••••" required />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="alert alert-info border-0 shadow-sm rounded-3">
            <i class="bi bi-info-circle-fill me-2"></i>
            Una vez registrado, su cuenta permanecerá inactiva hasta que confirme su correo electrónico a través del
            enlace de activación que se enviará a su bandeja de entrada.
          </div>

          <div class="d-flex justify-content-end gap-2 pt-3 border-top">
            <a href="/user/register-select" class="btn btn-warning rounded-pill px-4 fw-bold">
              <i class="bi bi-arrow-left"></i>
              Atrás
            </a>

            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary rounded-pill px-4 fw-bold">
              <i class="bi bi-person-check"></i>
              Registrarse
            </button>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>